<h2>Your password has been changed</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>This is a confirmation that the password for your account at <strong>{{appName}}</strong> has just been successfully changed.</p>

<p>You can now log in to your account using your new password.</p>

<div style='margin: 25px 0;'>
  <a href='{{appUrl}}/login' style='background-color: #667eea; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;'>Log in to your
    account</a>
</div>

<div class='divider'></div>

<p style='color: #999999; font-size: 14px;'>
  <strong>Important:</strong>
  If you did not change your password, it means someone has gained unauthorized access to your account. In that case, please contact us immediately at:
  <a href='{{appUrl}}/contact' style='color: #667eea;'>{{appName}}</a>.
</p>